Class NeutronLoadBalancerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opendaylight.controller.configuration.ConfigurationObject

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class NeutronLoadBalancerListener
extends ConfigurationObject
implements java.io.Serializable
    OpenStack Neutron v2.0 Load Balancer as a service (LBaaS) bindings. See OpenStack Network API v2.0 Reference for description of the fields: Implemented fields are as follows: id uuid-str default_pool_id String tenant_id uuid-str name String description String shared Bool protocol String protocol_port String load_balancer_id String admin_state_up Boolean status String http://docs.openstack.org/api/openstack-network/2.0/openstack-network.pdf
